casebody.data:
T-MOBILE SOUTH, LLC, petitioner,
v.
CITY OF ROSWELL, GEORGIA. No. 13-975. Supreme Court of the United States May 5, 2014.

Case below, 731 F.3d 1213.

Motion of Competitive Carriers Association for leave to file a brief as amicus curiae granted. Petition for writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the Eleventh Circuit granted.
